{"tid":308346,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【afterschool】一個簡單既方法減輕你既拖延症","createTime":"2017-07-04T05:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T13:35:59.000Z","uid":20848,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c2095f1349ba0106e974034e73fcc05357fe027","tid":308346,"uid":20848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:47:14.000Z","msg":"咁我平時就有睇唔同有關productivity 同 brain performance既書，今日想同大家分享一個簡單而有用既方法去幫助大家提升集中力同工作效率。<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法應該都唔少人聽過，叫做<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Pomodoro Technique</span></strong>（蕃茄工作法）。簡單黎講就係每工作25分鐘，就會有一個5分鐘既short break，而每過左4個「25分鐘」就會有一個15分鐘既long break。下圖係簡單既illustration:<br />\n<img src=\"http://afterschoolcommunity.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/PomodoroImage.001-2-768x432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fafterschoolcommunity.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FPomodoroImage.001-2-768x432.jpg&h=4bd8291c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n背後科學原理好簡單，因為好多研究都指出人類正常既集中時間係20-30分鐘，所以每25分鐘就應該要休息一下再繼續，確保可以keep住個腦既performance係最高既水平。<br />\n<br />\n當然睇落好似好簡單，但其實背後都有D技巧同重點要留意番：<br />\n1. 果25分鐘講緊係100%集中去做你既工作，唔可以分心，所以強烈建議大家將手機轉做勿擾模式。記住，覆個whatsapp都唔叫做100%集中，呢樣十分重要。<br />\n2. 果5分鐘休息時間都好重要，基本上係做咩都得，但就係呢段時間內一定唔可以再諗同岩岩果樣工作有關既野。記住呢段時間係比你個腦休息，可以趁呢休息覆下whatsapp睇下facebook等等，但我建議大家最好起身行下飲杯水，令個血液循環好D。<br />\n3. 每當25分鐘或者5分鐘既計時一響，要即刻停低你手上既野開始工作，唔好抱住「睇埋呢條片先」或「覆埋呢個message先」既心態去使用呢個technique。<br />\n<br />\napp store 同 google store都有好多免費既apps去幫你運用pomodoro technique，自己有興趣既download個黎試下。<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩想問或者分享既都可以comment下，有錯勿插。 <br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n咁其實我就搞緊個online learning platform去為中學生提供唔同既學習資訊、免費補習影片，主要係因為我並唔認同現時既補習、學習風氣，想透過一個平台去改善呢個問題。我而家就由簡單既blog post, facebook page, instagram等開始分享唔同既資訊。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家仲有興趣睇多D呢類型既內的，不妨like下我既facebook page或instagram支持一下。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/afterschoolcommunity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fafterschoolcommunity&d=9ujqSdPTjp82XUn4rxHLY04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=33700608\" target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/afterschoolcommunity</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/afterschoolcommunity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fafterschoolcommunity&d=9ujqSdPTjp82XUn4rxHLY04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=af56b3ee\" target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/afterschoolcommunity</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://www.afterschoolcommunity.com/blog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.afterschoolcommunity.com%2Fblog&d=9ujqSdPTjp82XUn4rxHLY04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=3e6ce00e\" target=\"_blank\">www.afterschoolcommunity.com/blog</a>"},{"pid":"e11be869ebebeeb1f3df2617144f5f54146c6567","tid":308346,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:14:41.000Z","msg":"留名再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63005bcda8a8de5d6232a1ddd466ba80d2192ac6","tid":308346,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:25:13.000Z","msg":"1已經做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b6a0ecc10d078c5f9d666e6627da97d12fb1dc","tid":308346,"uid":71900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:28:41.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b372fed0f25f7d4491af772ec42e207d6f3e04c9","tid":308346,"uid":41430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:33:02.000Z","msg":"平時專心5分鐘  休息25分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e16413a3b911de58113bab3cef56ba5e07dc9d","tid":308346,"uid":20848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T07:46:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1已經做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實都係，25分鐘聽落好短，但要你真係專心focus去工作真係唔易，因為身邊實在太多distraction, 但呢樣野正正就係要去改善既野。<br />\n<br />\n好簡單你試下開飛行模式，心無雜念去做25分鐘野。千奇唔好覺得秒回係必然，因為好多時候你都係同你d fd講下無聊野吹下水，但你一句我一句既時候時間好快會過。<br />\n<br />\n所以第一步你要有個心態「唔洗秒回人」，減少自己check 手機既次數，關哂d notification。<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你！btw like like 個page<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/afterschoolcommunity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fafterschoolcommunity&d=9ujqSdPTjp82XUn4rxHLY04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=33700608\" target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/afterschoolcommunity</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/afterschoolcommunity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fafterschoolcommunity&d=9ujqSdPTjp82XUn4rxHLY04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=af56b3ee\" target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/afterschoolcommunity</a>"},{"pid":"c4c51b9ea52a50c51b1b6e434c3b6e110ba289f8","tid":308346,"uid":20848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時專心5分鐘  休息25分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同我個fd講既野一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但咁樣落去真係唔掂，但改變習慣呢d野急唔黎，嘗試比自己一個細目標先，例如10分鐘唔用手機之後可以用2分鐘，再一步一步調節至適合自己既步伐！ 希望幫到你！<br />\n<br />\nBtw有興趣知多D既 like like我個page，睇樓上！thanks."},{"pid":"3b4b45acf1161ab324c47847506f29d3185630a4","tid":308346,"uid":1644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T07:48:59.000Z","msg":"求app名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce83254dfda220df84ffa48891e7435534889f34","tid":308346,"uid":20848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求app名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你用開咩機，上apps store search pomodoro, 頭幾個選一個簡單睇落岩你既就得！"},{"pid":"84ecfdc8cc0bfbfbf9fd630e9270f