lown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nfeel到再多幾次25分鐘就會不行了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我自己都會成日睇時間，但信我慢慢會越黎越好。但其實呢25分鐘工作5分鐘休息既節奏唔一定要照做，你可以根據你自己既習慣去調節，保持番個比例就ok. <br />\n<br />\n例如你覺得25分鐘太長可以先試下20分鐘工作4分鐘休息，再慢慢加長每節間長度。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e60f694d95023189c7e1d5595bdb2e5eccd1f5bd","tid":308346,"uid":47356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1已經做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔該你死左佢, 唔好拖人類後腿"},{"pid":"b6997745ddb8301d510a66cefe06c0ec3ca5e509","tid":308346,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:25:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3b92a79f5c2ff6679b2c2434ca4c535cbe4a6e9","tid":308346,"uid":20848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:35:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1已經做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔該你死左佢, 唔好拖人類後腿</blockquote><br />\n屌得好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/yJIyvJ6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyJIyvJ6.gif&h=e2f1bd41&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢位巴打好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}